{"title":"红岩魂——写在歌乐山渣滓洞","authors":["刘萱"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":4,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红岩魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写在歌乐山渣滓洞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘萱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时，在最有生命的山谷里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天都消失生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烙铁红透了黑夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面贴满了血腥的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出生的气息，火的呻吟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲不出去，冲不出去啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有三天，才会见到黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的屈辱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的苦争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如这即将被推倒的黑暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还想在最后这三天矗立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑暗不想倒下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日已经升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，便有了一个黎明前的大屠杀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连孩子也不放过的扫射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和这永不瞑目的红岩魂……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":16,"page_end":16}